Octodrag: "I've been waiting. Welcome to our love nest!"

Octodrag: "Since you've come here, it seems you've made up your mind
to become my wife."
Pony Celes: (When I look closely, it's definitely impossible...)
Pony Celes: (My strength is draining... Can I even fight this guy?)
Pony Celes: (No, no, no! Pull yourself together, me!)

Pony Celes: (He's not an octopus. He's just a weak, pathetic
monster. Not an octopus! Not an octopus!)
Octodrag: "Hm? What are you muttering about?"
Pony Celes: "This place is for everyone to enjoy!"
Pony Celes: "It's not a place for you to be!"
Pony Celes: "Get out of here right now!"
Octodrag: "No! No! This is our love nest!"
Octodrag: "It's a sacred place where you will bear my children!"
Pony Celes: "Don't joke with me. Who would bear your children?!"

Octodrag: "Muki---! How can you say such a super handsome guy like me
is disgusting?!"

Octodrag: "To think you could become the wife of such a handsome man,
you should feel like the luckiest person in the world!"
Pony Celes: "You keep saying 'handsome, handsome' but..."

Pony Celes: "Where do you see handsome... Have you never looked at
your own face in the mirror?"

Pony Celes: "Anyway... You're disgusting! Your speech, your
attitude, and your face! Everything!"

Octodrag: "Even if it's you, there are things that are okay to say and
things that are not!"

Octodrag: "It can't be helped... It seems you need a little punishment
until you change your heart."

Pony Celes: "After all... No, no good..."

Octodrag: "If only you had behaved yourself, none of this would have

Octodrag: "Now, let's cultivate our love together."

Octodrag: "If you've come to interfere in our love nest without

Ginga: "I'm with you! Let's fight together!"
Pony Celes: "Why do I have to be Pony Celes..."
Ginga: "Right now, defeating Zydagr is our priority!"

Pony Celes (Ginga's hands are trembling... He's enduring his fear to
come to my aid.)

Pony Celes (Ginga mustered up the courage to help me, and here I am

Pony Celes (Stupid, stupid, stupid! Pull yourself together, me!)

Pony Celes (What kind of hero am I if I can't protect the people

Pony Celes: "I'll turn you into takoyaki and eat you up!"

Pony Celes: "Ah, I take that back! I forgot I'm not good with
takoyaki!"
Ginga: "Haha, you're getting back to your usual self."

back. I'll handle this fight on my own!"
